Several years back Scott Ballard went the the hassle of figuring
out how to make a QAbstractItemModel work and was kind enough to
share a concise example.

http://www.riverbankcomputing.com/pipermail/pyqt/2009-April/022729.html

This has formed the beginnings of CANopyner and Scott was kind
enough to allow me to freely use his work in this project.  Thanks!
